name: VoteICT.org
description:
VoteICT.org is a free service that delivers election information to voters in the Wichita, KS area via text message.

---

This file is where the VoteICT.org homepage design and additional brand assets are managed. By publishing this project to the Figma Community, we hope to inspire designers in Wichita and beyond to get involved by contributing their ideas, talents, and time to this worthwhile effort.

Not from Wichita? VoteICT.org is open source, so feel free to use these designs or the Github repository below to jumpstart your own local project!

---

See the Github repository at https://github.com/devict/voteict
